  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Users of Breezy candy will utilize the candy's abrasiveness to scrape tongue surface. The
      scraping action together with the release of compounds contained inside the abrasive
      microcapsules will result in significant reduction of oral halitosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
